                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        stream-signing-keys-delete-key
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        DELETE Delete key 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Deleting a key revokes all signed URLs generated with the key.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        DELETE accounts/:account_identifier/stream/keys/:identifier
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        cURL (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        curl -X DELETE "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/9a7806061c88ada191ed06f989cc3dac/stream/keys/5213cfa121f70b8c1380686ffc371ba3" \
     -H "X-Auth-Email: user@example.com" \
     -H "X-Auth-Key: c2547eb745079dac9320b638f5e225cf483cc5cfdda41" \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Response (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        {
  "success": true,
  "errors": [],
  "messages": [],
  "result": ""
}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Stream Subtitles/Captions
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Add subtitles or captions to Stream videos for any language.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        stream-subtitles/captions
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Object definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        View properties and constraints defined on the object
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Show definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        stream-subtitles/captions-upload-a-caption/subtitle
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        PUT Upload a caption/subtitle 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Upload the file to the endpoint for a specific BCP47 language. One caption/subtitle per language is allowed.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        PUT accounts/:account_identifier/stream/:video_identifier/captions/:language
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Required parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Name /typeDescription /exampleConstraints
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        file
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        WebVTT file to upload
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        "@/Users/kyle/Desktop/tr.vtt"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          cURL (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          curl -X PUT "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/9a7806061c88ada191ed06f989cc3dac/stream/ea95132c15732412d22c1476fa83f27a/captions/tr" \
     -H "X-Auth-Email: user@example.com" \
     -H "X-Auth-Key: c2547eb745079dac9320b638f5e225cf483cc5cfdda41" \
     --form 'file=@/Users/kyle/Desktop/tr.vtt'
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Response (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          {
  "success": true,
  "errors": [],
  "messages": [],
  "result": {
    "label": "Trke",
    "language": "tr"
  }
}

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Stream Webhook
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Create a webhook to notify your service when videos are ready to stream.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          stream-webhook
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Object definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          View properties and constraints defined on the object
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Show definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          stream-webhook-create-a-webhook
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          PUT Create a webhook 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          PUT accounts/:account_identifier/stream/webhook
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Required parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Name /typeDescription /exampleConstraints
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          notificationUrl
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          string (url)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          The URL the webhooks will be sent to
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          "https://example.com"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            cURL (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            curl -X PUT "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/023e105f4ecef8ad9ca31a8372d0c353/stream/webhook" \
     -H "X-Auth-Email: user@example.com" \
     -H "X-Auth-Key: c2547eb745079dac9320b638f5e225cf483cc5cfdda41" \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     --data '{"notificationUrl":"https://example.com"}'
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Response (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            {
  "success": true,
  "errors": [],
  "messages": [],
  "result": {
    "notificationUrl": "https://example.com",
    "modified": "2014-01-02T02:20:00Z",
    "secret": "0b1c2423aa030a11583c6ffadda57fad681d00cd"
  }
}

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Stream Watermark Profile
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            You can create watermark profile for different videos.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            stream-watermark-profile
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Object definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            View properties and constraints defined on the object
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Show definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            stream-watermark-profile-create-a-watermark-profile-from-an-url
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            POST Create a Watermark Profile from an URL 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            You can create a watermark profile by specifying the URL to the image.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            POST accounts/:account_identifier/stream/watermarks
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Required parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Name /typeDescription /exampleConstraints
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            url
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            The source URL to the image where it was downloaded from. If the watermark profile was created via direct upload, this field will be null.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "https://company.com/logo.png"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Optional parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Name /typeDescription /exampleConstraints
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            A short description for the profile.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "Marketing Videos"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • default value: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            opacity
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            number
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Translucency of the image. 0.0 means completely transparent, and 1.0 means completely opaque. Note that if the image is already semi-transparent, setting this to 1.0 will not make it completely opaque.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            0.75
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • default value: 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • min value:0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • max value:1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            padding
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            number
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Whitespace between the adjacent edges (determined by position) of the video and the image. 0.0 means no padding, and 1.0 means padded full video width or length, determined by the algorithm.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            0.1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • default value: 0.05
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • min value:0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • max value:1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            scale
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            number
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            The size of the image relative to the overall size of the video. This parameter will adapt to horizontal and vertical videos automatically. 0.0 means no scaling (use the size of the image as-is), and 1.0 fills the entire video.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            0.1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • default value: 0.15
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • min value:0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • max value:1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            position
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Location of the image. Valid positions are: "upperRight", "upperLeft", "lowerLeft", "lowerRight", and "center". Note that "center" will ignore the "padding" parameter. 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "center"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • default value: upperRight
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            cURL (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            curl -X POST "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/023e105f4ecef8ad9ca31a8372d0c353/stream/watermarks" \
     -H "X-Auth-Email: user@example.com" \
     -H "X-Auth-Key: c2547eb745079dac9320b638f5e225cf483cc5cfdda41" \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     --data '{"url":"https://company.com/logo.png","name":"Marketing Videos","opacity":0.75,"padding":0.1,"scale":0.1,"position":"center"}'
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Response (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            {
  "success": true,
  "errors": [],
  "messages": [],
  "result": {
    "uid": "ea95132c15732412d22c1476fa83f27a",
    "size": 29472,
    "height": 600,
    "width": 400,
    "created": "2014-01-02T02:20:00Z",
    "downloadedFrom": "https://company.com/logo.png",
    "name": "Marketing Videos",
    "opacity": 0.75,
    "padding": 0.1,
    "scale": 0.1,
    "position": "center"
  }
}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            stream-watermark-profile-create-a-watermark-profile-via-basic-upload
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            POST Create a Watermark Profile via Basic Upload 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            You can create a watermark profile using a single HTTP POST (multipart/form-data) request.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            POST accounts/:account_identifier/stream/watermarks
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Required parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Name /typeDescription /exampleConstraints
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            file
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Image file to upload
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "@/Users/rchen/Downloads/watermark.png"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Optional parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Name /typeDescription /exampleConstraints
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              A short description for the profile.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              "Marketing Videos"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • default value: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              opacity
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              number
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Translucency of the image. 0.0 means completely transparent, and 1.0 means completely opaque. Note that if the image is already semi-transparent, setting this to 1.0 will not make it completely opaque.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              0.75
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • default value: 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • min value:0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • max value:1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              padding
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              number
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Whitespace between the adjacent edges (determined by position) of the video and the image. 0.0 means no padding, and 1.0 means padded full video width or length, determined by the algorithm.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              0.1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • default value: 0.05
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • min value:0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • max value:1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              scale
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              number
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              The size of the image relative to the overall size of the video. This parameter will adapt to horizontal and vertical videos automatically. 0.0 means no scaling (use the size of the image as-is), and 1.0 fills the entire video.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              0.1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • default value: 0.15
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • min value:0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • max value:1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              position
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Location of the image. Valid positions are: "upperRight", "upperLeft", "lowerLeft", "lowerRight", and "center". Note that "center" will ignore the "padding" parameter. 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              "center"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • default value: upperRight
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • read only
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              cURL (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              curl -X POST "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/023e105f4ecef8ad9ca31a8372d0c353/stream/watermarks" \
     -H "X-Auth-Email: user@example.com" \
     -H "X-Auth-Key: c2547eb745079dac9320b638f5e225cf483cc5cfdda41" \
     --form 'file=@/Users/rchen/Downloads/watermark.png' \
     --form 'name=Marketing Videos' \
     --form 'opacity=0.75' \
     --form 'padding=0.1' \
     --form 'scale=0.1' \
     --form 'position=center'
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Response (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              {
  "success": true,
  "errors": [],
  "messages": [],
  "result": {
    "uid": "ea95132c15732412d22c1476fa83f27a",
    "size": 29472,
    "height": 600,
    "width": 400,
    "created": "2014-01-02T02:20:00Z",
    "downloadedFrom": "https://company.com/logo.png",
    "name": "Marketing Videos",
    "opacity": 0.75,
    "padding": 0.1,
    "scale": 0.1,
    "position": "center"
  }
}

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Worker Script
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              A Worker script is a single script that is executed on matching routes in the Cloudflare edge
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              For more detailed documentation on using the API for Workers see the Workers API.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              worker-script
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Object definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              View properties and constraints defined on the object
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Show definition
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              worker-script-upload-worker
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              PUT Upload Worker permission needed: com.cloudflare.edge.worker.script.create
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Upload a worker, or a new version of a worker.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              PUT accounts/:account_identifier/workers/scripts/:script_name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              cURL (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              curl -X PUT "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/9a7806061c88ada191ed06f989cc3dac/workers/scripts/this-is_my_script-01" \
     -H "X-Auth-Email: user@example.com" \
     -H "X-Auth-Key: c2547eb745079dac9320b638f5e225cf483cc5cfdda41" \
     -H "Content-Type: application/javascript" \
--data "addEventListener('fetch', event => { event.respondWith(fetch(event.request)) })"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Response (example)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              {
  "success": true,
  "errors": [],
  "messages": [],
  "result": {
    "script": "addEventListener('fetch', event => { event.respondWith(fetch(event.request)) })",
    "etag": "ea95132c15732412d22c1476fa83f27a",
    "size": 1024,
    "modified_on": "2017-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  }
}
